				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Loan-Giang-hi%E1%BB%87p-t%C3%A1-tr%C3%AD-s%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%C3%BA-T%C3%BAc-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-phi%E1%BA%BFm-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-tp5Ifg9EPdUT8JpJ-f6z_w">Hoạ Loan Giang hiệp tá trí sự Đỗ Phú Túc tiên sinh trung thu dạ phiếm nguyên vận - 和灣江協佐致事杜富肅先生中秋夜泛原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-B%C3%A0ng/Ho%C3%A1n-kh%C3%AA-sa-Phi%E1%BA%BFm-chu-ho%C3%A0n-D%C6%B0-Anh-qu%C3%A1n/poem-e_s-l5-L_ebrraYSPX9s5g">Hoán khê sa - Phiếm chu hoàn Dư Anh quán - 浣溪沙－泛舟還餘英館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mao-B%C3%A0ng/author-PevYJ4ZQTa8nQsmeM0lQIQ">Mao Bàng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/H%E1%BB%93i-chu/poem-5LrKEzvRtiImdMC1JT8tkQ">Hồi chu - 回舟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Mai-hoa-thanh-V%C5%A9-Hoa-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-DJM93MXTnd9Vo7_nH3wF4w">Mai hoa thanh - Vũ Hoa đài - 賣花聲－雨花臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%AD-Ho%C3%A0/Ng%C6%B0-ca-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-W0IGstZn6UgYVwNXwDotWw">Ngư ca tử kỳ 3 - 漁歌子其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%AD-Ho%C3%A0/author-K-KPc0BUQdzcRKS-f2QraA">Trương Chí Hoà</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/Ng%C6%B0-ti%E1%BB%81u-canh-m%E1%BB%A5c-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-tqaAeYB44GM-6noFGeVNMw">Ngư tiều canh mục kỳ 2 - 漁樵耕牧其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/author-0zxx9ptNwfX9AYtkCUmYYQ">Ninh Tốn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-Qu%E1%BB%B7-M%C3%B4n-quan/poem-R2FZcfRWYRa9C2WY-s8eIw">Nhập Quỷ Môn quan - 入鬼門關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thu%C3%BD-Hoa-s%C6%A1n/poem-JyokTsUCXU7xNWft5ka9IQ">Thuý Hoa sơn - 翠花山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%C3%ACnh-%C4%91%C3%AA/poem-hB8fSbFWEVPCh6MSACVxmw">Tình đê - 晴堤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BA%A1n-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%91%C3%A0m/poem-FCM74bDLavoCiqDZWjGGsw">Vạn Trượng đàm - 萬丈潭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
